I can tell by that look in your eyes.

00:34:57.570 --> 00:34:58.420
An Lan,

00:34:59.340 --> 00:35:01.170
I might get better soon.

00:35:01.420 --> 00:35:02.530
Of course.

00:35:02.850 --> 00:35:04.900
I can see
you're getting better and better.

00:35:04.900 --> 00:35:06.240
Do you remember

00:35:06.340 --> 00:35:08.220
our pinky promise?

00:35:09.050 --> 00:35:10.050
Which one?

00:35:10.780 --> 00:35:12.640
Being each other's bridesmaids.

00:35:15.010 --> 00:35:16.300
Of course I remember.

00:35:16.820 --> 00:35:18.090
You need to hurry up.

00:35:18.090 --> 00:35:19.260
Don't count on me.

00:35:20.340 --> 00:35:21.610
You need to hurry.

00:35:22.880 --> 00:35:24.880
I'm afraid I can't wait much longer.

00:35:25.220 --> 00:35:26.570
What are you saying?

00:35:26.570 --> 00:35:29.230
Didn't you just say
you're getting better soon?

00:35:29.700 --> 00:35:31.090
Fifty-fifty.

00:35:31.820 --> 00:35:33.620
What do you mean by fifty-fifty?

00:35:35.940 --> 00:35:38.670
Remember to send me
your recent medical records.

00:35:38.790 --> 00:35:40.520
I'll take a look at them for you.

00:35:41.460 --> 00:35:42.980
I have to give it a shot.

00:35:44.430 --> 00:35:45.800
I must take this chance.

