Didn't I just tell you?

00:36:00.610 --> 00:36:01.780
The 5th.

00:36:04.380 --> 00:36:05.170
The 5th.

00:36:07.530 --> 00:36:08.650
The 5th is good.

00:36:09.170 --> 00:36:09.970
Remember

00:36:09.970 --> 00:36:11.740
to send me

00:36:11.740 --> 00:36:12.910
your recent test results.

00:36:12.910 --> 00:36:15.310
I'll have specialists
look at them for you.

00:36:18.450 --> 00:36:19.340
Wanqing,

00:36:19.860 --> 00:36:22.520
have you changed
to another hospital recently?

00:36:30.910 --> 00:36:31.710
What's wrong?

00:36:31.900 --> 00:36:33.560
I found two big pieces of news.

00:36:33.700 --> 00:36:35.260
Jiang Yuwen once had a daughter.

00:36:35.260 --> 00:36:36.460
You won't believe it,

00:36:36.570 --> 00:36:37.610
but Jiang Yuwen's wife

00:36:37.610 --> 00:36:39.740
died shortly
after their daughter was born.

00:36:39.740 --> 00:36:40.820
Jiang Yuwen was focused
entirely on his research

00:36:40.820 --> 00:36:42.700
and had no ability to raise a child.

00:36:42.700 --> 00:36:43.530
So he gave the child

00:36:43.530 --> 00:36:45.730
to a couple who couldn't have children.

00:36:45.970 --> 00:36:47.420
Both parties kept it very confidential,

00:36:47.420 --> 00:36:49.170
so almost nobody knows about it.

00:36:49.170 --> 00:36:49.940
But

00:36:50.220 --> 00:36:52.950
I just found the adoption records
from back then.

00:36:53.260 --> 00:36:53.940
So,

00:36:54.420 --> 00:36:56.050
we all know this girl.

00:36:56.570 --> 00:36:57.490
Tang Xin?

00:37:00.010 --> 00:37:02.010
Tang Xin is Jiang Yuwen's daughter?

00:37:11.470 --> 00:37:13.160
In the cake bombing case,

00:37:13.700 --> 00:37:15.340
Tang Xin was indeed
one of the three survivors

00:37:15.340 --> 00:37:17.010
at Moma Group.

00:37:21.420 --> 00:37:22.940
If Jiang Yuwen is Squid,

00:37:23.490 --> 00:37:24.700
there's no way he'd want his daughter

00:37:24.700 --> 00:37:25.700
to get hurt.

00:37:26.450 --> 00:37:27.860
But is he really Squid?

00:37:27.940 --> 00:37:28.610
Boss.

00:37:30.460 --> 00:37:31.060
Boss!

00:37:32.650 --> 00:37:33.380
Um,

00:37:33.380 --> 00:37:36.010
has mass surveillance
located Jiang Yuwen yet?

